**Example Log Output (DANGEROUS)**:
```text
{"level":"info","message":"Login attempt","requestBody":{"username":"john.doe","password":"MySecretP@ss123!","rememberMe":true},"headers":{"authorization":"Bearer eyJhbG..."}}
{"level":"info","message":"User john.doe attempting login with password MySecretP@ss123!"}
{"level":"info","message":"Login successful for john.doe, token: eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9..."}
