public class SanitizingPatternLayoutEncoder extends PatternLayoutEncoder {

    private static final Pattern SENSITIVE_PATTERN = Pattern.compile(
        "(?i)(password|secret|token|key|authorization)[\\s]*[=:][\\s]*[^\\s,;\"']+"
    );

    @Override
    public byte[] encode(ILoggingEvent event) {
        String originalMessage = event.getFormattedMessage();
        String sanitizedMessage = SENSITIVE_PATTERN.matcher(originalMessage)
            .replaceAll("$1=[REDACTED]");

        // This is a simplified example - production would need custom event wrapper
        return super.encode(event);
    }
}
```

**Defense in Depth Layers**:

1. **Field-Level Annotation Marking**:
